PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774555873
OL,3,CDoctor caught using dead father's
OL,4,Cdisabled blue badge to park for free
OL,6,F"The Council takes all suspected fraud
OL,7,Fand misuse of blue badges extremely
OL,8,Fseriously and will not hesitate to
OL,9,Finvestigate all reports and, where it
OL,10,Fis possible, progress cases to
OL,11,Fprosecution.
OL,13,F"The size of the fines issued should
OL,14,Fbe deterrent enough for anybody
OL,15,Fconsidering the fraudulent use of blue
OL,16,Fbadges in Reading."
OL,26,@xD@SO]
